# OpenWithFlash
This batch scripts enables opening SWF files with the Flash Player projector.
# Installation
Download the file.\
Run the batch file with administrative privileges (scroll down for instructions), and wait.\
# Administrator privileges
Run Command Prompt as administrator.\
